Magic ledger API:

    (Dummy)
    --------------------------------
    GET     /createDummy

    (Core)
    --------------------------------
    GET     /blocks
    GET     /blocks/index/:index
    GET     /blocks/hash/:hash
    POST    /transaction
                > :sender
                > :recipient
                > :amount

    (Mining)
    --------------------------------
    GET     /mine-blocks/:minerAddress
    POST    /submit-block
                > :
